response.overview: I got a pickle! I got a pickle! I got a pickle! HEY! HEY! HEY! HEY! On this episode of Hitting the Highspots the wrestling wonder known as Rob Naylor sits down with two thirds of the Rascalz, Zachary Wentz and Dezmond Xavier.  The Rascalz are one of the fastest rising professional wrestling acts in the entire world. Putting on epic matches everywhere they go. Our host dives deep into their career and talking all things past, present, and future. Who are some of their biggest influences? What are some of their dream matches? Find out on this wild episode of Hitting the Highspots!
response.title: Hitting The Highspots - The Rascalz
